title: Little Boots - some tracks
description:
Some tracks by Little Boots (third attempt):

Little Boots - Stuck On Repeat (Studio version)
Little Boots - Stuck On Repeat (BBC Radio Live Session)
Little Boots - Meddle (BBC Radio Live Session)
Little Boots - Stuck On Repeat (YouTube version)
Little Boots - Meddle (YouTube version)
Little Boots - Hot Chip (YouTube version)
Little Boots - Wearing My Rolex (YouTube version)

File type: 128kb MP3 (but all but the first is ripped from internet streaming video)
Total file size: 35 MB

The BBC Radio version of Meddle is horrendously over-produced and sucks, oh well. The versions ripped from YouTube obviously suffer from low audio quality. Also I can't tell if she actually has any talent as a musician or whether she's just fit. Does it matter?
